#ad Ladies and gentlemen, it’s officially time to crown the ULTIMATE Flamin’ Hot champ! After tallying up the Flamin’ Hot Faceoff results, #TeamDoritos has been announced the winner – but if you ask me, #TeamCheetos is still number one!! I mean who doesn’t love Cheetos Flamin’ Hot Spicy Pepper Puffs and the swag from their Flamin’ Hot Capsule Collection?
 
To help us all cool off a little from this fierce rivalry, @cheetos is giving one lucky fan an iced out watch on July 12. Follow & comment on @cheetos IG post using #FlaminHotFaceOff and #sweepstakes
